> 	3.17
> to the following releases:
> 	4.9.331 4.14.296 4.19.262 5.4.220 5.10.150 5.15.75 5.19.17 6.0.3 6.1
> is vulnerable, and anything newer than that (i.e. any kernel newer than
> August of 2022) is just fine.
